{"id":"258","name":"bright-early-best-week-ever-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Best Week Ever Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2008-06-02T09:00:00-05:00","tags":["bbq","bush-mccain challenge","cma music festival","georgia tech bulldogs","lipscomb university","moveon.org","Nashville","nashville mta","nashville pride","nashville sounds","oklahoma sooners","tennessee","vanderbilt university"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-259\" title=\"2543128240_7560f1043f\" src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/06/2543128240_7560f1043f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"357\"></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. What a weekend, huh? Some of us took an <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/30/take-an-urban-dare-and-hit-the-streets-this-saturday/\" target=\"_blank\">Urban Dare</a> on Saturday while some were out in Franklin <a href=\"http://twitter.com/recreate/statuses/824139828\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;twitter.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">raving about</a> the best BBQ in the world, and it seems like we didn&#x2019;t get any sleep with all that <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/brandonjames/2542830308/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">thunder and ruckus</a> on Saturday night. A couple of us are still recovering from sweating it out at the park yesterday for <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/29/take-pride-in-20-years-nashville-pride-2008/\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville Pride</a> and the search for the elusive &#x201C;Special Edition&#x201D; <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/29/lets-try-this-again-special-edition-bush-mccain-challenge/\" target=\"_blank\">Bush-McCain Challenge</a> which we think stood us up <em>again</em>. And of course, the motherland turned 212. We don&#x2019;t anticipate things slowing down either, with the <a href=\"http://www.cmafest.com/2008/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.cmafest.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">CMA Music Festival</a> turning the place upside down for the rest of the week. Luckily Nashvillest is here to get you through the week, and we&#x2019;ll be doing our best to stay on top of it all so you don&#x2019;t miss a thing.</p><ul><li><strong>One small step.</strong> It seems like everyone&#x2019;s going green these days. And well, everyone is trying to figure out how to get out of paying so much for gas. Always on the cutting edge (ha, ha, ha), Nashville MTA will be <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080601/GREEN02/806010407/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">adding six hybrid buses</a> to the fleet by the end of the year.</li><li><strong>Worthy effort</strong>. We were all excited about Lipscomb and Vandy both having teams in the NCAA tournament this year, but they were both eliminated this weekend. <a href=\"http://www.nashvillecitypaper.com/news.php?viewStory=60568\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Vandy fell</a> to the Oklahoma Sooners in an 11-10 heartbreaker, and Georgia <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080601/SPORTS060403/80601006/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">took down Lipscomb</a> 14-3.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces</strong>. Coyote makes an impromptu appearance <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/16439207/detail.html?rss=nash&amp;psp=news\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">near Vandy</a> &#x2026; Guy robs a Trinity Lane Family Dollar with a <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=8406800\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">stolen bulldozer</a> &#x2026; Gallatin man taken to Vanderbilt University Medical Center after <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080531/NEWS03/80531003/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">standoff</a> in girlfriend&#x2019;s trailer &#x2026; Sounds <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=8336061\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">replace</a> their GM.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/scribebytrade/2543128240/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">christyfrink</a>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}